": "issue_comment", "id": 41836759}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/2083/comments/48648080.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/issues/2083#comment-48648080"}}, "issue": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/2083.json"}}, "type": "issue", "id": 2083, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{51a0cd5d-8697-4eb1-8b08-e919ee881e1c}ts=1694483"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "gazebo", "full_name": "osrf/gazebo", "uuid": "{51a0cd5d-8697-4eb1-8b08-e919ee881e1c}"}, "title": "Point and spot lights don't cast shadows"}, "content": {"raw": "Similar issue for Ignition Rendering: https://bitbucket.org/ignitionrobotics/ign-rendering/issues/32/point-and-spot-lights-dont-cast-shadows", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>Similar issue for Ignition Rendering: <a href=\"https://bitbucket.org/ignitionrobotics/ign-rendering/issues/32/point-and-spot-lights-dont-cast-shadows\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"ap-connect-link\">https://bitbucket.org/ignitionrobotics/ign-rendering/issues/32/point-and-spot-lights-dont-cast-shadows</a></p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2018-10-30T17:48:26.188848+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Louise Poubel", "uuid": "{5cfa2075-477b-4ded-bdb9-8d2479544ec4}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B5cfa2075-477b-4ded-bdb9-8d2479544ec4%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B5cfa2075-477b-4ded-bdb9-8d2479544ec4%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:6ff86fcb-b7ab-44a5-b8a6-f6d9cae8b6e8/7d903d90-c5ea-4182-b7ef-0d467e9e1c74/128"}}, "nickname": "chapulina", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:6ff86fcb-b7ab-44a5-b8a6-f6d9cae8b6e8"}, "updated_on": null, "type": "issue_comment", "id": 48648080}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/2083/comments/49254745.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/issues/2083#comment-49254745"}}, "issue": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/2083.json"}}, "type": "issue", "id": 2083, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{51a0cd5d-8697-4eb1-8b08-e919ee881e1c}ts=1694483"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "gazebo", "full_name": "osrf/gazebo", "uuid": "{51a0cd5d-8697-4eb1-8b08-e919ee881e1c}"}, "title": "Point and spot lights don't cast shadows"}, "content": {"raw": "Hello everyone,\n\nI'm working on some simulations where shadows from the lights are somehow important. Do you have any perspective to finish this enhancement soon?\n\nJust let me know if you need some help.\n\nThanks!", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>Hello everyone,</p>\n<p>I'm working on some simulations where shadows from the lights are somehow important. Do you have any perspective to finish this enhancement soon?</p>\n<p>Just let me know if you need some help.</p>\n<p>Thanks!</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2018-12-03T11:55:35.513286+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Bruno Pereira", "uuid": "{ed944783-5002-4305-a5c4-43e6c536d210}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7Bed944783-5002-4305-a5c4-43e6c536d210%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7Bed944783-5002-4305-a5c4-43e6c536d210%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ee167b83b22eeda3ea55cec23ef1a1e0d=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsBP-0.png"}}, "nickname": "brschettini", "type": "user", "account_id": "5ad63ae6926ac92a7c0de030"}, "updated_on": null, "type": "issue_comment", "id": 49254745}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/2083/comments/52255218.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/issues/2083#comment-52255218"}}, "issue": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/2083.json"}}, "type": "issue", "id": 2083, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{51a0cd5d-8697-4eb1-8b08-e919ee881e1c}ts=1694483"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "gazebo", "full_name": "osrf/gazebo", "uuid": "{51a0cd5d-8697-4eb1-8b08-e919ee881e1c}"}, "title": "Point and spot lights don't cast shadows"}, "content": {"raw": "In my case, directional light doesn\u2019t cast shadow neither, maybe because I use Intel and AMD GPU. Is there any workaround? a plugin? I know Gazebo maintainer and developer are busy so I want to implement it myself, I just don\u2019t know how.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>In my case, directional light doesn\u2019t cast shadow neither, maybe because I use Intel and AMD GPU. Is there any workaround? a plugin? I know Gazebo maintainer and developer are busy so I want to implement it myself, I just don\u2019t know how.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2019-05-23T10:26:39.186904+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Achmad Fathoni", "uuid": "{cbc5d55b-20d9-4d80-971b-6892209bcb72}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7Bcbc5d55b-20d9-4d80-971b-6892209bcb72%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7Bcbc5d55b-20d9-4d80-971b-6892209bcb72%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/27eed661aec82a1165f45b6259af5f00d=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsAF-2.png"}}, "nickname": "achmad-fathoni", "type": "user", "account_id": "5ce61cf6a67da10dbe9daca7"}, "updated_on": "2019-05-23T10:27:58.448866+00:00", "type": "issue_comment", "id": 52255218}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/2083/comments/52577428.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/issues/2083#comment-52577428"}}, "issue": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/2083.json"}}, "type": "issue",